{"tid":1886912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[Condom大省] 湖北外全國新增確診15連降！新增出院首超新增確診數！","createTime":"2020-02-19T08:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T17:40:46.000Z","uid":65371,"like":100,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"ecabf2d72538cb107951c53b55d812f40990ed60","tid":1886912,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T08:22:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1079656165742524&amp;id=393304404377707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1079656165742524%26id%3D393304404377707&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=f23ec43c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1079656165742524&amp;id=393304404377707</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xc2Sg2T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxc2Sg2T.jpg&h=c46fb6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據今日國家衛健委和湖北衛健委公布的疫情最新情況，包含好幾個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好消息</span></span>：<br />\n <br />\n一、新增出院人數首次超過新增確認。昨日全國新增確診病例1749例，新增治愈出院病例1824例。<br />\n <br />\n二、現有確診病例數開始下降。昨日全國確診病例57805，而17日此數據為58016例，開始呈下降態勢。<br />\n <br />\n三、全國新增治愈出院病例已連續7天超千人。昨日此數據為1824例。<br />\n <br />\n四、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全國除湖北以外地區新增確診病例56例，連續第15日呈下降態勢，亦是連續兩天降至兩位數。</span></span><br />\n <br />\n五、湖北除武漢外新增確診降為兩位數。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">希望好消息越來越多！</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6jttfQwuGGc0uIVanBs59A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2F6jttfQwuGGc0uIVanBs59A&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=032fce77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/6jttfQwuGGc0uIVanBs59A</a><br />\n <br />\n----------<br />\n <br />\n歡迎關注公署官方微信公眾號(帳號:fmcoprc)，希望為你提供豐富有益的資訊和便捷周到的服務。"},{"